    "Along with T, the prompt also includes the task's description C. Finally, we instruct the META-AGENT to select an appropriate set of tools T s (T s ⊂ T) to wait for synthesizing trajectories.",
    "The prompt we use for automatic tool selection can be seen in Appx.",
    "Trajectories Synthesis.",
    "Without depending on closed-source models, we enable the META-AGENT to synthesize planning trajectories on its own.",
    "Equipped with T s, we instruct the META-AGENT to synthesize trajectories in a zero-shot manner on the database D adhering to the format of Thought-Action-Observation as defined in Yao et al. (2023)."
